msgstr "WordPress 阅读能力"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:74
msgid "Read-only WordPress site, content, and structure abilities."
msgstr "只读 WordPress 站点、内容和结构能力。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:80
msgid "WordPress Page Abilities"
msgstr "WordPress 页面功能"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:81
msgid "Read-only WordPress page discovery and inspection abilities."
msgstr "只读 WordPress 页面发现和检查能力。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:87
msgid "WordPress Diagnostics"
msgstr "WordPress 诊断"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:88
msgid "Redacted WordPress environment diagnostics for Abilities API clients."
msgstr "编辑了 Abilities API 客户端的 WordPress 环境诊断。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:94
msgid "Workflow Recipe Definitions"
msgstr "工作流程配方定义"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:95
msgid ""
"Read-only workflow recipe definitions for host-side ability composition."
msgstr "host 端能力组合的只读工作流程配方定义。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:189
msgid "List Workflow Recipes"
msgstr "列出工作流程食谱"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:190
msgid ""
"Returns read-only workflow recipe definitions for host-side ability "
"composition without executing workflow steps."
msgstr "返回 host 端能力组合的只读工作流配方定义，而不执行工作流步骤。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:212
msgid "Get Workflow Recipe"
msgstr "获取工作流程配方"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:213
msgid ""
"Returns one read-only workflow recipe definition by recipe id or case id "
"without executing workflow steps."
msgstr "按配方 ID 或案例 ID 返回一个只读工作流程配方定义，而不执行工作流程步骤。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:233
msgid "List Media"
msgstr "列出媒体"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:234
msgid "Returns a paginated list of media library attachments."
msgstr "返回媒体库附件的分页列表。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:279
msgid "Resolve Media Attachment By URL"
msgstr "解决媒体附件：URL"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:280
msgid ""
"Resolves a same-site uploads URL to bounded media attachment candidates with "
"read-only match evidence."
msgstr "解析同一站点将 URL 上传到具有只读匹配证据的有限媒体附件候选。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:327
msgid "List Terms"
msgstr "列出条款"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:328
msgid "Returns a paginated list of terms for a taxonomy."
msgstr "返回分类项的分页列表。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:371
msgid "List Taxonomy Terms"
msgstr "列出分类项"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:372
msgid ""
"Returns a paginated term list for one taxonomy, including parent information."
msgstr "返回一种分类的分页术语列表，包括父级信息。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:418
msgid "List Categories"
msgstr "列出类别"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:419
msgid "Returns a paginated list of post categories."
msgstr "返回文章类别的分页列表。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:449
msgid "List Tags"
msgstr "列出标签"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:450
msgid "Returns a paginated list of post tags."
msgstr "返回文章标签的分页列表。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:480
msgid "Get Term"
msgstr "获取期限"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:481
msgid "Returns details for one taxonomy term by id or slug."
msgstr "按 id 或 slug 返回一个分类项的详细信息。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:510
msgid "List Comments"
msgstr "列出评论"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:511
msgid "Returns a paginated list of comments."
msgstr "返回分页的评论列表。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:553
msgid "Resolve Internal Link Targets"
msgstr "解析内部链接目标"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:554
msgid ""
"Finds local published content that can serve as internal-link targets for a "
"post draft or optimization workflow."
msgstr "查找可用作后期草稿或优化工作流程的内部链接目标的本地发布内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:599
msgid "Build Inline Image Blocks"
msgstr "构建内联图像块"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:600
msgid ""
"Converts uploaded inline image rows into append-ready Gutenberg image blocks "
"without writing post content."
msgstr "将上传的内嵌图像行转换为可追加的 Gutenberg 图像块，而不写入文章内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:635
msgid "Build Media SEO Assets"
msgstr "构建媒体 SEO 资产"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:636
msgid ""
"Builds a canonical media SEO enrichment asset list from article media "
"workflow upload outputs."
msgstr "根据文章媒体工作流程上传输出构建规范媒体 SEO 丰富资产列表。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:668
msgid "GEO Analysis"
msgstr "GEO 分析"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:669
msgid ""
"Builds deterministic GEO and AI visibility issues, recommendations, and "
"evidence from article text."
msgstr "从文章文本中构建确定性的 GEO 和 AI 可见性问题、建议和证据。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:701
msgid "Optimize Media Metadata"
msgstr "优化媒体元数据"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:702
msgid ""
"Builds deterministic media title, alt, caption, description, source, and "
"disclosure suggestions from article and media context."
msgstr "根据文章和媒体上下文构建确定性媒体标题、替代项、说明文字、描述、来源和披露建议。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:735
msgid "Position Inline Image Blocks"
msgstr "定位内联图像块"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:736
msgid ""
"Places generated inline image blocks after matching paragraph, heading, or "
"anchor targets and falls back to append."
msgstr "在匹配段落、标题或锚点目标之后放置生成的内联图像块，然后回退到附加。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:771
msgid "Build Article Optimization Report"
msgstr "构建文章优化报告"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:772
msgid ""
"Composes SEO, GEO, internal-link, and media optimization sections into one "
"deterministic report."
msgstr "将 SEO、GEO、内部链接和媒体优化部分组成一份确定性报告。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:807
msgid "Build SEO Report Context"
msgstr "构建 SEO 报告上下文"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:808
msgid ""
"Builds lightweight deterministic SEO issues and recommendations for article "
"optimization workflows."
msgstr "为文章优化工作流程构建轻量级确定性 SEO 问题和建议。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:840
msgid "Read Post Optimization Context"
msgstr "阅读文章优化上下文"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:841
msgid ""
"Reads a post title, excerpt, content, slug, categories, tags, SEO fields, "
"template, and format snapshot for article optimization workflows."
msgstr "读取文章标题、摘录、内容、slug、类别、标签、SEO 字段、模板和格式快照以进行文章优化工作流程。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:872
msgid "Build Article Single Optimization Suggest"
msgstr "构建文章单个优化建议"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:873
msgid ""
"Builds one canonical single-article optimization suggestion envelope for "
"title, taxonomy, excerpt, slug, SEO, content, and GEO improvements."
msgstr "为标题、分类、摘录、slug、SEO、内容和 GEO 改进构建一个规范的单篇文章优化建议信封。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:914
msgid "Build Article Optimization Apply Plan"
msgstr "构建文章优化应用计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:915
msgid ""
"Builds one conservative apply plan from the read-only article optimization "
"report without applying writes."
msgstr "根据只读文章优化报告构建一个保守的应用计划，而不应用写入。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:950
msgid "Compose Article Optimization Apply Result"
msgstr "撰写文章优化应用结果"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:951
msgid ""
"Composes report, apply plan, safe apply result, and remaining advisory "
"changes into one deterministic envelope."
msgstr "将报告、应用计划、安全应用结果和剩余建议更改写入一个确定性信封中。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:984
msgid "Extract Reference Post Style"
msgstr "提取参考文章样式"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:985
msgid ""
"Reads reference posts and returns a compact writing-style profile for "
"article workflows."
msgstr "阅读参考文章并返回文章工作流程的紧凑写作风格配置文件。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1032
msgid "Extract Site Style Baseline"
msgstr "提取站点样式基线"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1033
msgid ""
"Extracts a lightweight site-wide or author-specific writing-style baseline "
"from recent posts."
msgstr "从最近的文章中提取轻量级的站点范围或特定于作者的写作风格基线。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1080
msgid "Build Article Production Fingerprint"
msgstr "构建文章生产指纹"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1081
msgid ""
"Builds a stable lightweight production fingerprint for article dedupe and "
"result summaries."
msgstr "为文章重复数据删除和结果摘要构建稳定的轻量级生产指纹。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1124
msgid "Check Article Production Duplicate"
msgstr "检查文章制作重复"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1125
msgid ""
"Checks whether a lightweight article production fingerprint already exists "
"on a post."
msgstr "检查文章上是否已存在轻量级文章生产指纹。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1152
msgid "Review Article Output Light"
msgstr "评论文章 输出光"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1153
msgid ""
"Builds lightweight local article quality, style, image, and AI-risk review "
"signals without model calls."
msgstr "无需模型调用即可构建轻量级本地文章质量、风格、图像和 AI 风险审核信号。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1190
msgid "Compose Article Production Result"
msgstr "撰写文章 制作结果"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1191
msgid ""
"Summarizes the article production mainline with result mode, degraded "
"reasons, fingerprint, handoff, and next action."
msgstr "总结文章生成主线，包括结果模式、降级原因、指纹、切换和下一步操作。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1226
msgid "Compose Article Draft Result"
msgstr "撰写文章草稿结果"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1227
msgid ""
"Composes one canonical draft workflow result with draft content, metadata "
"resolution, shared SEO/GEO review, and handoff hints."
msgstr "使用草稿内容、元数据解析、共享的 SEO/GEO 审核和移交提示组成一份规范的草稿工作流程结果。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1263
msgid "Resolve Article Publication Decision"
msgstr "解决文章发表决定"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1264
msgid ""
"Resolves a deterministic article publish, schedule, review, or draft handoff "
"after quality and duplicate checks."
msgstr "解决质量和重复检查后的确定性文章发布、计划、审阅或草稿移交问题。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1302
msgid "Build Article Style Profile"
msgstr "建立文章风格档案"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1303
msgid ""
"Merges baseline, reference, and explicit writing-style hints into one "
"lightweight article style profile."
msgstr "将基线、参考和明确的写作风格提示合并到一个轻量级的文章风格配置文件中。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1339
msgid "List Pages"
msgstr "列表页"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1340
msgid ""
"Lists WordPress pages with status, parent, search, sorting, and pagination "
"filters."
msgstr "列出带有状态、父级、搜索、排序和分页过滤器的 WordPress 页面。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1372
msgid "Get Page"
msgstr "获取页面"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1373
msgid ""
"Returns a single WordPress page, including content, template, hierarchy, "
"author, and optional meta."
msgstr "返回单个 WordPress 页面，包括内容、模板、层次结构、作者和可选元。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1419
msgid "Inspect Page Structure"
msgstr "检查页面结构"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1420
msgid ""
"Inspects WordPress page hierarchy, template usage, and orphaned parent "
"relationships without modifying pages."
msgstr "在不修改页面的情况下检查 WordPress 页面层次结构、模板使用情况和孤立父关系。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1449
msgid "List Pages Tree"
msgstr "列表页面树"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1450
msgid ""
"Returns a hierarchical page tree for navigation and site-structure review."
msgstr "返回用于导航和站点结构审查的分层页面树。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1490
msgid "Get Content Publishing Checklist"
msgstr "获取内容发布清单"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1491
msgid ""
"Returns a deterministic pre-publish readiness checklist for one post or page "
"without applying changes."
msgstr "返回一篇文章或页面的确定性预发布准备清单，而不应用更改。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1535
msgid "Get Content Inventory Health"
msgstr "获取内容库存健康状况"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1536
msgid ""
"Scans a bounded content inventory and summarizes missing titles, thin "
"content, excerpt gaps, media gaps, SEO metadata gaps, and stale content."
msgstr "扫描有限的内容清单并总结缺失的标题、薄弱的内容、摘录差距、媒体差距、SEO 元数据差距和过时的内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1581
msgid "Get Nonproduction Content Inventory"
msgstr "获取非生产内容清单"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1582
msgid ""
"Detects bounded smoke, fixture, and nonproduction content that may distort "
"content, taxonomy, comment, and operations diagnostics without mutating the "
"site."
msgstr "检测可能扭曲内容、分类、评论和操作诊断而不改变站点的有限烟雾、固定装置和非生产内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1615
msgid "Build Nonproduction Content Cleanup Plan"
msgstr "制定非生产内容清理计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1616
msgid ""
"Builds a read-only cleanup plan for detected nonproduction content, mapping "
"each candidate to existing governed write abilities without trashing or "
"deleting anything."
msgstr "为检测到的非生产内容构建只读清理计划，将每个候选内容映射到现有的受控写入能力，不移入回收站，也不删除任何内容。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1650
msgid "Build Content Inventory Fix Plan"
msgstr "制定内容库存修复计划"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1651
msgid ""
"Maps bounded content inventory issues to reviewable fix actions that reuse "
"existing governed write abilities without mutating posts."
msgstr "将有限的内容库存问题映射到可审查的修复操作，这些修复操作可重用现有的受控写入功能，而无需更改文章。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1685
msgid "Get Bulk Publishing Checklist"
msgstr "获取批量发布清单"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1686
msgid ""
"Runs the read-only publishing checklist for a bounded list of posts and "
"returns batch readiness totals."
msgstr "运行有限的文章列表的只读发布清单并返回批次准备情况总计。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1732
msgid "Get Internal Link Opportunity Report"
msgstr "获取内部链接机会报告"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1733
msgid ""
"Builds a post-id based internal-link opportunity report with candidate "
"targets, anchor suggestions, and placement hints."
msgstr "构建基于文章 ID 的内部链接机会报告，其中包含候选目标、锚点建议和放置提示。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1773
msgid "Get Site Operations Dashboard"
msgstr "获取站点操作仪表板"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1774
msgid ""
"Builds a bounded read-only site operations dashboard for content status, "
"inventory issues, taxonomy health, comments, and media signals."
msgstr "为内容状态、库存问题、分类健康状况、评论和媒体信号构建有界只读站点操作仪表板。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1803
msgid "Get Post Publish Risk Report"
msgstr "获取发布后风险报告"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1804
msgid ""
"Builds a read-only publish risk report for one post from checklist, SEO/GEO, "
"revision, and internal-link signals."
msgstr "根据清单、SEO/GEO、修订和内部链接信号为一篇文章构建只读发布风险报告。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1834
msgid "Get Article Publish Preflight Context"
msgstr "获取文章 发布 预检上下文"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1835
msgid ""
"Aggregates post context, publishing checklist, publish risk, workflow "
"context, and calendar context for host-side publish preflight workflows "
"without writing."
msgstr "聚合发布上下文、发布清单、发布风险、工作流上下文和日历上下文，以供 host 端发布预检工作流而不写入。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1867
msgid "Get Content Refresh Opportunities"
msgstr "获得内容刷新机会"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1868
msgid ""
"Scans a bounded content set and returns stale, thin, SEO-light, answer-"
"light, and low-link refresh opportunities."
msgstr "扫描有界内容集并返回陈旧、稀疏、SEO-light、answer-light 和低链接刷新机会。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1900
msgid "Get Old Article Refresh Context"
msgstr "获取旧文章刷新上下文"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1901
msgid ""
"Aggregates refresh opportunities, SEO/GEO gaps, site style baseline, "
"internal-link graph health, and optional selected-post link opportunities "
"for host-side old article refresh workflows."
msgstr "聚合 host 端旧文章刷新工作流程的刷新机会、SEO/GEO 差距、网站样式基线、内部链接图运行状况以及可选的选定文章链接机会。"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1935
msgid "Get Internal Link Graph Health"
msgstr "获取内部链接图健康状况"

#: includes/Packages/Core_Read_Package.php:1936
msgid ""
"Scans a bounded content set and summarizes outgoing links, incoming links, "
"orphan posts, and candidate internal-link pairs."
